snippet.title: Wildmender Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wildmender comes to Xbox Series X|S on 28 September 2023, and is available for preorder today!

In this desert gardening survival game, start from a tiny spring and cultivate a blooming garden. Explore a vast world amid the sands and uncover its mysteries with up to four-player online multiplayer. Can you defend against the relentless forces of nature and mysterious wraith corruption, to bring life to a dying world?

https://www.xbox.com/games/store/wildmender/9NRWLT874D38/0010
